<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.1">
<l>polika polika polika pōyiṟṟu valluyirc cāpam</l>
<l>naliyu narakamum nainta namaṉukkiṅ kiyātoṉṟu millai</l>
<l>kaliyuṅ keṭuṅkaṇṭu koḷmiṉ kaṭalvaṇṇaṉ pūtaṅkaṇ maṇmēl</l>
<l>maliyap pukunticai pāṭi yāṭi yuḻitarak kaṇṭōm</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May [he] prosper, prosper, prosper. Gone is the curse of harsh life.</l>
<l>Hell dwindles, for shrinking Yama there is nothing here,</l>
<l>and the Kali [aeon] will be over. See for yourselves: the bhūtas of the ocean-coloured one</l>
<l>we have seen enter on earth in numbers, sing music, dance [and] wander about.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
